## Image Generation Prompts

### Prompt 1: In-Game Chibi Sprite (Reference Sheet)
*(Feed approved Pomegraknight illustration as reference image. Describe only pose and motion.)*

Chibi pixel art sprite sheet, front-facing full body, isolated on black background. Nine frames arranged in a single row: Idle, Walk, Jump, Slash1, Slash2, Slash3, Blush, SeedErupt, FireTornado. Same character design as the reference. All animations energetic and aggressive — wide stances, fast transitions, visible impact.
* **Idle:** Feet planted wide, sword held at the ready. Slight bouncing weight shift — eager, impatient energy. Sharp grin.
* **Walk:** Determined march, sword gripped in both hands. Moderate stride, upper body leans slightly forward. Not a stroll — she's going somewhere.
* **Jump:** Explosive upward launch, knees pulled up high, sword raised overhead ready to strike downward. No hesitation.
* **Slash1:** Wide horizontal sweep, sword arcs from right to left across the body, weight shifting into the swing.
* **Slash2:** Quick reverse slash, backhand return swing, tighter and faster than Slash1.
* **Slash3:** Heavy two-handed downward cleave, sword raised high then driven down with full body weight. The finisher.
* **Blush:** Both fists clenched at sides, head thrown back, body engulfed in flames bursting outward. A power-up roar.
* **SeedErupt:** Arms flung upward, body crouched slightly, seeds spraying outward in an arc from behind/above her.
* **FireTornado:** A rapid spinning motion — body becomes a blur of rotation, sword extended outward, flames spiraling around her into a vortex. First, she crouches slightly and plants her feet, then her body winds into the spin, sword carving a continuous horizontal circle at waist height. Flames trail the blade seamlessly, forming a full tornado cylinder around her. The last frames show the spin decelerating, flames receding, body settling back into a grounded stance.

### Prompt 2: Character Poster
*(Feed approved Pomegraknight illustration as reference image. Describe only pose, expression, and composition.)*

Character poster, same design as the reference image. Pomegraknight stands in a wide, grounded combat stance, short sword held in one hand and resting across her shoulder. Her expression is fierce — sharp grin, eyes bright with battle hunger. Flames curl around her shoulders and forearms without consuming her — she is in control of the fire. Behind her, an arc of pomegranate seeds hangs suspended mid-air, some glowing with ember light. Dark background with deep red and orange rim lighting. The overall feeling: a warrior who runs toward danger, not away from it.

